Author: CeslieLondon
Text: Toasted pbj is god sent. I’m just commenting because nobody else appreciates it like me so I’m glad you do. A delicacy. Don’t feel bad, I’m honestly so happy for you. Sometimes I get my fix with Sara Lee 45 cal bread, sugar free jelly, and pb2. A depression sandwich but it helps numb the pain lol
